        "type": "message",
        "text": "This is such an important topic! So much content marketing advice comes from companies selling marketing software -- so the people writing the content are also SMEs. The rest of us doing content for people that are not also marketers have a very different set of challenges and IMO it is something our profession has been sort of hand waving away for years.",
